{"tid":904928,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣門將 : 旅外機會,Gary White一直在替他注意","createTime":"2018-11-16T17:31:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-18T07:59:59.000Z","uid":62257,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"22bbd00dfa2e8cae0c9f5645b40dfb0b3f63f00a","tid":904928,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T17:31:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20181116004730-260403\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20181116004730-260403&d=6c610CMsiqVX8lnycmZZXwEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=6450f844\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20181116004730-260403</a><br />\n<br />\n中華男足沒能拿到隊史首張東亞4強決賽門票，但對香港、北韓都能hold住局面，門神潘文傑更是屢屢救險，堪稱中華隊本屆賽事的MVP。潘文傑賽後表示，就算無法晉級，也要為台灣支持足球的人全力以赴，他會持續自我要求，繼續爭取旅外機會。<br />\n<br />\n「今天一開始還是想贏，到後來體力下滑，要攻也不是很有利，選擇用守的方式。」儘管今天只要不輸3球，就能保送前教頭蓋瑞懷特（Gary White）目前執教的香港隊晉級4強，但潘文傑強調，並不是為了別人而拚這場比賽。<br />\n<br />\n「今天就是要給台灣支持足球的人，就是為了我們自己、為了台灣而拚。」潘文傑說：「不是要幫助什麼球隊，就盡力守，不要再擴大比分、不要失更多球，把比分壓低，或許還有進球的機會。」<br />\n中華隊總教練王家中賽後稱讚潘文傑本屆表現有目共睹，展現強烈的求勝意志，光是從體重身形上的控制，就看得出這位門將自我要求的決心。事實上在雅加達亞運之前，潘文傑就把體重降到80公斤左右，儘管後來要再降體重會很困難，但他已經把體脂率從12％降到9％左右，在東亞盃展現靈活身手。<br />\n「自從懷特帶領的團隊後，我一直記錄他們訓練的方式和細節，雖然我的球隊沒有守門員教練，但我會和搭檔討論要怎麼練，把以前留下來的東西繼續保持。」潘文傑說，旅外機會懷特一直在替他注意，礙於有些國家在聯賽優先保護自家守門員，並不接受外援，旅外機會比較難，但他一直沒有放棄這個目標。"},{"pid":"22ee5ca91ba061e6cadf6946bccb703f496c7134","tid":904928,"uid":62257,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T17:35:01.000Z","msg":"要引用基督教一句: 神使萬事互相效力<br />\n多得Gary White 深得潘文傑嘅愛戴<br />\n喺佢離開後， 佢嘅前子弟兵 反而幫番佢而家帶嘅隊<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/即時體育/260135/港足-東亞錦直擊-黃洋獲選mvp-要傳承披港戰衣的榮譽感\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E9%AB%94%E8%82%B2%2F260135%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%B6%B3-%E6%9D%B1%E4%BA%9E%E9%8C%A6%E7%9B%B4%E6%93%8A-%E9%BB%83%E6%B4%8B%E7%8D%B2%E9%81%B8mvp-%E8%A6%81%E5%82%B3%E6%89%BF%E6%8A%AB%E6%B8%AF%E6%88%B0%E8%A1%A3%E7%9A%84%E6%A6%AE%E8%AD%BD%E6%84%9F&d=6c610CMsiqVX8lnycmZZXwEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=93ea010f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/即時體育/260135/港足-東亞錦直擊-黃洋獲選mvp-要傳承披港戰衣的榮譽感</a><br />\n<br />\n中華台北門將潘文傑場上多次救出險球，讓港隊得以晉級，賽後一眾港將亦上前「致謝」。（袁志浩攝）<br />\n<a href=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2104067/org/bd09ff46e479b5c22e2d6703c61f63ad.jpg/ugZLWC30-4S4n5uKtJSTxKUkGLUQq0z3pPNpDY7zaQ0?v=w1440\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2104067%2Forg%2Fbd09ff46e479b5c22e2d6703c61f63ad.jpg%2FugZLWC30-4S4n5uKtJSTxKUkGLUQq0z3pPNpDY7zaQ0%3Fv%3Dw1440&d=6c610CMsiqVX8lnycmZZXwEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=e64b02bb\" target=\"_blank\">https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2104067/org/bd09ff46e479b5c22e2d6703c61f63ad.jpg/ugZLWC30-4S4n5uKtJSTxKUkGLUQq0z3pPNpDY7zaQ0?v=w1440</a>"},{"pid":"295b424dacfe121dcc2ee47433e2da57464cee7e","tid":904928,"uid":62257,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T17:35:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2104067/org/bd09ff46e479b5c22e2d6703c61f63ad.jpg/ugZLWC30-4S4n5uKtJSTxKUkGLUQq0z3pPNpDY7zaQ0?v=w1440\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2104067%2Forg%2Fbd09ff46e479b5c22e2d6703c61f63ad.jpg%2FugZLWC30-4S4n5uKtJSTxKUkGLUQq0z3pPNpDY7zaQ0%3Fv%3Dw1440&h=8dab40a9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5d4eefc5c2cfc76af1689b8be3567326abb4721e","tid":904928,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T18:04:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"608cbc4a377ec389bd28509acb300cec7ed5ac90","tid":904928,"uid":14983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T18:06:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad41f619cf057a0cee8934ed47b34a258dec8fd1","tid":904928,"uid":204180,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T19:34:26.000Z","msg":"睇黎佢真係好崇拜，或者感激白咖喱"